videos.description: Jahvon Quinerly drives to the basket and switches hands midair to avoid the defender and make the impressive layup in traffic.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Alabama's Jahvon Quinerly switches hands for sweet layup) 2022/01/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Alabama's Jahvon Quinerly switches hands for sweet layup

videos.description: Auburn's Dylan Cardwell elevates to grab the missed shot and hammers home a powerful dunk with authority.

videos.headline: Dylan Cardwell throws down huge putback slam for Auburn

videos.description: Wendell Green drives and tosses a quick lob to Devan Cambridge, who goes up for the emphatic slam for Auburn.

videos.description: With the defender all over him, JD Davison is still able to contort his body to get off an awkward wild shot that somehow goes in for an and-1 bucket.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (How did JD Davison make this and-1 layup?) 2022/01/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: How did JD Davison make this and-1 layup?

videos.description: JD Davison drives to the basket and winds up to hammer down an epic one-handed dunk right in the face of a 7-foot defender.
